00:17:05.300 --> 00:17:07.010
Quoi ? Une fusion ?

00:17:13.850 --> 00:17:17.700
Faites place au plus grand guerrier du royaume de drum.

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:26.880
Chess marimo !

00:17:27.820 --> 00:17:30.830
