00:17:31.000 --> 00:17:32.420
Trop fort !

00:17:32.580 --> 00:17:34.000
C'est pourri, oui !

00:17:34.790 --> 00:17:36.680
Restez bien sur vos gardes.

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:43.590
